********************
Desktop Installation
********************

Instructions for setting up GNOME with VNC on OCI.

Install GNOME
-------------

.. code-block::

    sudo yum groupinstall "GNOME Desktop" "Graphical Administration Tools"
    sudo reboot
    sudo passwd opc

Connect to instance
-------------------

1. Add ssh key to OCI console under 'Console Connections'.
2. Copy VNC Connection into terminal
3. Connect by 'localhost:5900'
4. Start desktop 'sudo systemctl isolate graphical.target'



